Description: Snow cover should come before clouds when searching for snow cover
V006 dataset should come before version 005
Soil moisture products should come before salinity products when searching for SMAP
Ancillary products should be below data products (can't reproduce locally)
OMI products should be above TOMS products because OMI is a later generation.
Collections with Leaf area index in the titles should show up before others when searching for leaf area index
ABoVE project collections should be ahead of collections with above in the description
NPP should return ecology results first
SMAP soil moisture searches should return L2-L4 SMAP above salinity products
SMAP soil moisture searches should return L2-L4 SMAP above L1 products
SMAP soil moisture searches should return L2-L4 SMAP above SMAPVEX products
SMAP L3 freeze/thaw products before anything else when searching for SMAP freeze/thaw
World glacier inventory should be a top 3 collection when searching for glacier
GLIMS should be a top 3 collection when searching for glacier
Northern Hemisphere EASE-Grid 2.0 Version 4 should be ranked high because temporal coverage is very long and community usage is high.
MODIS/Terra Snow Cover 5-Min L2 Swath 500m V006 should be ranked high because Global spatial coverage and long temporal coverage, continuously updated, and community usage is high.
